SXDrive 0.4.5 includes minor improvements and cosmetic fixes:
- fix handling of selective synchronization (Settings -> Selective sync)
- improve download notifications
- don't show the list of volumes in the systray menu (go to Settings -> Volumes for the list of available volumes)
- show transfer direction for files in Settings -> Activity
- support configuration link format of Skylable SX 1.1
- improve installation and upgrades on Windows
- try to work-around filesystem watcher issues on OS X
